msgid "fleshed wire gate"
msgstr "肉化鐵絲網門"

#. ~ Description for fleshed wire gate
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A chain gate with flesh covering most of the hole. It has a visible padlock "
"mechanism, and opening it may require you to remove all the gore in it."
msgstr "一個鏈式門，大部分孔洞被血肉覆蓋。它有一個可見的掛鎖機制，打開它可能需要清除所有內部的血肉。"

#. ~ Description for fleshed wire gate
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A chain gate with flesh covering most of the hole."
msgstr "一個鏈式門，大部分孔洞被血肉覆蓋。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed pink wall"
msgstr "肉化粉色牆壁"

#. ~ Description for fleshed pink wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "Wall painted pink, adorned by gore and veins."
msgstr "粉刷成粉色的牆壁，裝飾著血肉和脈絡。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed reinforced glass door"
msgstr "肉化強化玻璃門"

#. ~ Description for fleshed reinforced glass door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced glass door infested by flesh. Opening it might be a minor "
"problem..."
msgstr "一扇被血肉侵染的強化玻璃門。打開它可能是個小問題……"

#. ~ Description for fleshed brick wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A sturdy brick wall with veins digging through the gaps, forming odd "
"patterns."
msgstr "一面堅固的磚牆，脈絡從縫隙中鑽出，形成奇怪的圖案。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed concrete wall"
msgstr "肉化混凝土牆"

#. ~ Description for fleshed concrete wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "An already unpleasant wall infected by the flesh."
msgstr "一面原本就令人不快的牆壁，被血肉感染了。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed metal wall"
msgstr "肉化金屬牆"

#. ~ Description for fleshed metal wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A thick, blast-proof metal wall overrun by the flesh. Now you've got more "
"time to take it down."
msgstr "一面厚實、防爆的金屬牆，被血肉覆蓋。現在你有更多時間來拆除它。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed metal floor"
msgstr "肉化金屬地板"

#. ~ Description for fleshed metal floor
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A metal floor overrun by horrid crimson flesh."
msgstr "一塊被可怕的血紅色血肉覆蓋的金屬地板。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed reinforced glass"
msgstr "肉化強化玻璃"

#. ~ Description for fleshed reinforced glass
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Thick, durable pane of reinforced glass infested by flesh. Not only it is "
"tough, it completely blocks the vision through it."
msgstr "一塊厚實、耐用的強化玻璃板，被血肉侵染。它不僅堅固，還完全阻擋了視線。"

