"A machine with several taps that dispenses clean water. Although, the flesh "
"clogs the dispenser, rendering it useless."
msgstr "一臺帶有多個水龍頭的機器，用於提供清潔水。然而，血肉堵塞了出水口，使其無法使用。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed ballistic glass"
msgstr "肉化防彈玻璃"

#. ~ Description for fleshed ballistic glass
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
