"Overrun by the flesh, this stacked up laminated glass is much tougher than "
"before."
msgstr "被血肉覆蓋，這疊層壓玻璃比以前更加堅固。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "card reader"
msgstr "讀卡器"

#. ~ Description for card reader
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"This is a smartcard reader. Engraved is a text saying \"Secronom Project\" "
"underneath a biohazard symbol. You'll definitely need a special keycard of "
"some sort to unlock the door."
msgstr "這是一個智能卡讀卡器。上面刻有文字，在生物危害符號下方寫著“Secronom項目”。你肯定需要某種特殊的鑰匙卡來解鎖這扇門。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\ter_furn.json
msgid "crunch!"
msgstr "嘎吱！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "whack!"
msgstr "啪！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "biohazard metal door"
msgstr "生物危害金屬門"

#. ~ Description for biohazard metal door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A galvanized steel door, forged to withstand punishment and impede anyone or"
" anything. Typically used in conjunction with automated electronic locking "
"mechanisms that require an external source to unlock. It has a biohazard "
"symbol and a card reader embedded to the door labeled \"Level 1 clearance\"."
msgstr ""
"一扇鍍鋅鋼門，鍛造以承受衝擊並阻擋任何人或物。通常與自動電子鎖定機制配合使用，需要外部來源才能解鎖。門上有一個生物危害符號和一個嵌入的讀卡器，標有“1級權限”。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\ter_furn.json
msgid "metal screeching!"
msgstr "金屬尖嘯聲！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\ter_furn.json
msgid "clang!"
msgstr "哐當！"

#. ~ Description for biohazard metal door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A galvanized steel door, forged to withstand punishment and impede anyone or"
" anything. Typically used in conjunction with automated electronic locking "
"mechanisms that require an external source to unlock. It has a biohazard "
"symbol depicting something unearthly on the other side... as the flesh "
"fibers crawl out of the edges. A card reader is embedded to the door, and it"
" requires a special key card for it to open."
msgstr ""
"一扇鍍鋅鋼門，鍛造以承受衝擊並阻擋任何人或物。通常與自動電子鎖定機制配合使用，需要外部來源才能解鎖。門上有一個生物危害符號，描繪了另一邊某種超自然的存在……因為血肉纖維從邊緣爬出。一個讀卡器嵌入在門上，需要特殊的鑰匙卡才能打開。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "experimental vat"
msgstr "實驗用容器"

#. ~ Description for experimental vat
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
