msgid "The tongue lost its grasp."
msgstr "舌頭鬆開了抓握。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then its muscles suddenly mutates!"
msgstr "隨後它的肌肉突然變異了！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "You've been constricted!"
msgstr "你被緊緊纏住了！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"After a brief moment, a temporary force field has been generated surrounding"
" the secronom dragon!"
msgstr "片刻之後，一個臨時力場在塞克諾姆龍周圍生成！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then several sparks of electric discharge archs through the vicinity!"
msgstr "隨後數道電弧在附近區域躍動！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then spews out flesh webs at their surroundings!"
msgstr "隨後向周圍噴吐出血肉蛛網！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then its dreadful inner mouth stretches its way to crunch at them!"
msgstr "隨後它那駭人的內嘴伸展而出，狠狠咬向他們！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"After a short period of time, the equinox flung its rancid flesh into the "
"sky!"
msgstr "短暫時間後，晝夜平分者將其腐臭的血肉拋向天空！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"Then suddenly, a flash flood of liquidated vile flesh were sent into a "
"direction!"
msgstr "隨後突然之間，一股液化惡臭血肉的洪流朝一個方向噴湧而去！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The flesilisk then suddenly spew its fang at them!"
msgstr "血肉蜥蜴突然朝他們噴吐尖牙！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"The flesilisk then undulates hastily, creating a hail of bone spikes in "
"every direction!"
msgstr "血肉蜥蜴隨後急促波動，向四面八方掀起一陣骨刺冰雹！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"For a short moment, the flesilisk's bone spikes shoots into the sky then "
"swoops down towards them!"
msgstr "短暫瞬間，血肉蜥蜴的骨刺射向天空，隨後俯衝而下襲向他們！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Flesilisk's body then barrages its bone spikes into them!"
msgstr "血肉蜥蜴的身體隨後用骨刺對他們進行猛烈轟擊！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"But suddenly its volatile core explodes violently, spreading corrupted acid everywhere!\n"
"<color_light_green>The corrupted devourer suffers from the explosion!</color>"
msgstr ""
"但突然其不穩定的核心猛烈爆炸，將腐蝕性酸液擴散到各處！\n"
"<color_light_green>腐化吞噬者因爆炸而受損！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"Then its arm biters vomit a large amount of polluted acid at their location!"
msgstr "隨後其手臂啃噬者向他們的位置嘔吐大量汙染酸液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"The corrupted devourer's core quickly forms numerous errant tendrils that "
"lashes towards them!"
msgstr "腐化吞噬者的核心迅速形成無數狂亂觸鬚，猛烈抽打向他們！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"But while the corrupted devourer looks at them, its arm biters suddenly eats"
" away the flesh it touches!"
msgstr "但當腐化吞噬者注視他們時，其手臂啃噬者突然開始啃噬所接觸的血肉！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then grows into a saddler!"
msgstr "隨後成長為鞍具怪！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then grows into a saddler brute!"
msgstr "隨後成長為鞍具怪蠻兵！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Then grows into a saddler scout!"
msgstr "隨後成長為鞍具怪斥候！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Suddenly it erupts into gore!"
msgstr "它突然爆裂成血肉！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"As the flesh trembles further, the tower's tentacle veins suddenly moves and"
" thrashes the entire area!"
msgstr "隨著血肉進一步震顫，高塔的觸手血管突然移動並橫掃整個區域！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Suddenly, the flesh heap discharges of blood acid!"
msgstr "突然，血肉堆噴發出血液酸液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The flesh heap's orifice spews out globs of blood acid!"
msgstr "血肉堆的孔口噴出團塊狀血液酸液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The air thickens as the shapeshifter moves."
msgstr "變形者移動時，空氣變得凝重。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Silhouettes were formed around the shapeshifter!"
msgstr "變形者周圍形成了剪影！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "An errant silhouette flies toward its target, then shreds them!"
msgstr "一道遊離的剪影飛向目標，然後將其撕碎！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "An errant silhouette rakes through their target!"
msgstr "一道遊離的剪影掠過目標！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"The shapeshifter sets out a harrowing shriek before reaping their target!"
msgstr "變形者發出駭人的尖嘯，隨後收割目標！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "A silhouette were formed before the shapeshifter!"
msgstr "一道剪影在變形者面前形成！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "Your spitter armament shoots a glob of blood acid!"
msgstr "你的噴吐武裝射出一團血液酸液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The amalgam stinger thrusts its stinger at them!"
msgstr "融合毒刺者用它的毒刺刺向他們！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The amalagam stinger slashes in a wide arc!"
msgstr "融合毒刺者揮出一記大範圍斬擊！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The fleshed stinger bursts a bulbous wart!"
msgstr "血肉毒刺者爆開一個球狀疣瘤！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The fleshed ravager's body bursts a chunk of flesh!"
msgstr "血肉掠奪者的身體爆出一大塊血肉！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "The fleshed ravager's extra appendages flings in every direction!"
msgstr "血肉掠奪者的額外附肢向四面八方甩動！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid "<color_yellow>The flesh heap (blade) slashes wildly!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>血肉堆（刃型）瘋狂劈砍！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>The flesh heap (blade) projects several bone "
"spikes!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>血肉堆（刃型）投射出數根骨刺！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>The flesh heap (tendril) sweeps its tentacle veins!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>血肉堆（觸鬚型）掃動它的觸手血管！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_effects.json
