"Thought it was known inferior to A7 laser rifle, SS laser rifle displays "
"efficiency in barraging shots for cheap UPS charges, along with its reduced "
"weight and volume."
msgstr "儘管被認為不如A7激光步槍，SS激光步槍在廉價UPS充電下進行連射時表現出高效能，同時重量和體積也有所減少。"

