#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "grubby zombie's bloated mouth"
msgid_plural "grubby zombie's bloated mouths"
msgstr[0] "蛆蟲殭屍的腫脹嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "Spits larger globs of tainted goo infested with parasites."
