msgid_plural "snatcher zombie's mouths"
msgstr[0] "攫取殭屍的嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid ""
"Sends off a long-ranged tongue with precise accuracy, stopping the target's "
"movement. Takes a long time to replenish before firing a new one."
msgstr "以精準的準頭發射一條長距離舌頭，阻止目標的移動。在發射新舌頭前需要很長時間補充。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "pellucid zombie's mouth"
msgid_plural "pellucid zombie's mouths"
msgstr[0] "透明殭屍的嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "An acid-dribbing mouth of a pellucid zombie. Spits concentrated acid."
msgstr "透明殭屍的滴酸嘴。吐出濃縮酸液。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_harvest.json
msgid ""
"With effort, you attempt to collect some worthy byproducts out of the "
"dragon."
msgstr "你努力嘗試從龍身上收集一些有價值的副產品。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sacrifice"
msgstr "獻祭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sacrifice'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster deals an instant death damage, sacrificing itself upon casting a spell that's been combined with.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者造成即死傷害，並在施放組合法術時犧牲自身。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "null"
msgstr "null"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'null'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "null... just ignore this."
msgstr "null... 忽略此項即可。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Charging Stance"
msgstr "蓄力姿態"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Charging Stance'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sets itself into guarding stance, blocking physical damage while gaining a burst of speed.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者進入防禦姿態，格擋物理傷害並獲得速度爆發。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid "a spell"
msgstr "一個法術"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a spell'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid ""
"Target spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster locks its line of sight onto the target, then casts the Spell(s).'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的目標法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者鎖定目標的視線，然後施放法術。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon Blood Vessel"
msgstr "召喚血管"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon Blood Vessel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its hands to create a blood vessel.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者引導雙手創造一條血管。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon 2 Blood Vessels"
msgstr "召喚2條血管"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 2 Blood Vessels'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its core to create 2 blood vessels.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者引導核心創造2條血管。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 2 Blood Vessels'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's blood wave creates 2 blood vessels nearby.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者的血浪在附近創造2條血管。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon Blood Fiend"
msgstr "召喚血魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon Blood Fiend'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's blood wave creates a blood fiend nearby.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者的血浪在附近創造一個血魔。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Blood Curl"
msgstr "血之捲曲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Curl'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'When the target is nearby, caster manipulates some of the blood wave's blood to stick into the target, applying even more bloodbath. This is casted 3 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'當目標靠近時，施法者操縱部分血浪中的血液附著於目標，施加更多浴血效果。此法術施放3次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Blood Wave"
msgstr "血浪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Wave'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its surrounding blood to strike a large area in a cone, dealing moderate bash damage and applying bloodbath to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者引導周圍血液以錐形區域攻擊大範圍，造成中等鈍擊傷害並對所有受影響生物施加浴血效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Explode"
msgstr "爆炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Explode'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster explodes, dealing bashing damage and applying bloodbath to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者爆炸，造成鈍擊傷害並對所有受影響生物施加浴血效果。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Explode'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster violently explodes, dealing bashing damage and applying bloodbath to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者猛烈爆炸，造成鈍擊傷害並對所有受影響生物施加浴血效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Writhing Slash"
msgstr "扭曲斬擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Writhing Slash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the caster's target is nearby after precision stab, the caster's tongue sweeps it sideways, dealing cutting damage and applies an unstable footing to the affected creatures. This is casted for 2 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'若精準刺擊後施法者的目標在附近，施法者用舌頭橫向掃擊，造成切割傷害並對受影響生物施加不穩立足效果。此法術施放2次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Precision Stab"
msgstr "精準刺擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Precision Stab'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster reaches and quickly strikes the target with its hideous tongue, dealing moderate stabbing damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者伸出其可怖的舌頭快速刺擊目標，造成中等穿刺傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Gas Burst"
msgstr "氣體爆發"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gas Burst'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the caster's target is upclose, caster sends a strong burst of acidic gas in a wide, yet short cone, dealing moderate acid damage to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'若施法者的目標貼近，施法者釋放一股強烈的酸性氣體，形成寬而短的錐形區域，對所有受影響生物造成中等酸蝕傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Noxious Gas"
msgstr "劇毒氣體"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Noxious Gas'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body to produce an acidic gas and sends it to the target in a narrow cone that deals lingering acid damage to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者引導身體產生酸性氣體，並以狹窄錐形區域射向目標，對所有受影響生物造成持續酸蝕傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Lock On"
msgstr "鎖定"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lock On'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster glares at the target, inflicting disorienting impairments.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者凝視目標，施加迷惑性減益效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Vein Explosion"
msgstr "血管爆炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vein Explosion'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'The torn up ligament explodes internally, dealing an extra bio damage to the target.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'撕裂的韌帶在內部爆炸，對目標造成額外的生物傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Volatile Scratch"
msgstr "易爆抓擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Volatile Scratch'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster scratches the target with a claw imbued in volatile bodily fluid, dealing moderate cutting damage that lingers for few turns.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者用浸染易爆體液的爪子抓擊目標，造成中等切割傷害，效果持續數回合。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
