msgid "Blood Suck"
msgstr "吸血"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Suck'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'More vine strands from the caster sweeps around the vicinity, collecting and sucking the blood fields in which heals the caster.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
