"'If the target is nearby, caster slashes with a vine, dealing moderate cutting damage. This is casted 2 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'如果目標在附近，施法者用藤蔓斬擊，造成中等切割傷害。此法術會施放2次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Razor Leaf"
msgstr "飛葉快刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Razor Leaf'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"(Combo) spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends its sharp leaves to mince the targets in a line, dealing moderate cutting damage.'"
msgstr ""
"（連擊）怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者發射鋒利的葉片，在一條線上切碎目標，造成中等切割傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sweet Scent"
msgstr "甜蜜香氣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sweet Scent'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Floral bloom accompanies the wild outburst, spreading sleep-inducing pollens in the same area.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'花朵盛開伴隨著狂野生長的爆發，在同一區域散佈誘導睡眠的花粉。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Wild Outgrowth"
msgstr "狂野生髮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Wild Outgrowth'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"(Combo) spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body to create an outburst of twisted roots and vines under the target, dealing moderate stabbing damage and ensnares all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"（連擊）怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者引導身體，在目標下方製造扭曲根鬚和藤蔓的爆發，造成中等穿刺傷害並纏繞所有受影響的生物。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon 2 Triffids"
msgstr "召喚2株三裂植物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 2 Triffids'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its hand to create and send forth 2 triffids, along with the wild outgrowth.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者引導其手部創造並派出2株三裂植物，同時伴隨狂野生髮。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Acid Touch"
msgstr "酸蝕之觸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Touch'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'When upclose, caster then scratches the target with its excess blood, dealing acid damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'近距離時，施法者用其過剩的血液抓擊目標，造成酸蝕傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Acid Coat"
msgstr "酸蝕塗層"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Coat'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its hands to extract a large amount of acidic fluid from its body, then sends it to the target in a short but wide line, dealing moderate acid damage that lingers overtime.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者通過雙手引導，從體內提取大量酸性液體，然後以短而寬的直線射向目標，造成持續的中等酸蝕傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sweepidic"
msgstr "掃蕩酸液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sweepidic'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the target is nearby, caster sweeps some of the excess fluids in a small cone, dealing small damage to all creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'如果目標在附近，施法者會以小錐形範圍掃出部分多餘液體，對所有生物造成輕微傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Acid Rain"
msgstr "酸雨"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Rain'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its whole body for a very long time to produce an extremely vast amount of corrosive bodily fluids and sends it up above the target then explodes, dealing tremendous acid damage to all creatures in the vicinity, which lingers within time.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者長時間引導全身，產生巨量腐蝕性體液，將其送至目標上方後爆炸，對範圍內所有生物造成巨大的酸蝕傷害，並隨時間持續生效。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Portal"
msgstr "傳送門"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Portal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'A multi-dimensional portal is made from the collapse. This portal leads the carrion race into the world.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'坍縮形成了一個多維傳送門。這個傳送門將腐屍種族引入世界。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Gravitational Collapse"
msgstr "引力坍縮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gravitational Collapse'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'After channeling for a massive amount of time, caster's gravitational force field collapses, creating a supernova, dealing tremendous bash damage to all creatures. Sparkling objects are scattered, which enlightens the area.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'經過長時間引導，施法者的引力場坍縮，產生超新星爆發，對所有生物造成巨大的鈍擊傷害。散落的閃光物體照亮了區域。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Portal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'A multi-dimensional portal is made from the collapse. This portal leads the vector race into the world.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'坍縮形成了一個多維傳送門。這個傳送門將矢量種族引入世界。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Vectorize"
msgstr "矢量化"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vectorize'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'A wave of vector dust spreads from the caster, converting nearby organic terrains such as grass and bushes to become infected.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'一股矢量塵埃從施法者處擴散，將附近的有機地形（如草地和灌木）轉化為感染狀態。'"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'a spell'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "The sight of <npcname> locks onto its target..."
msgstr "<npcname>的視線鎖定了目標..."

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Morph"
msgstr "形態轉變"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Morph'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster violently morphs into an ichorus.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者猛烈地轉變為一隻伊科魯斯。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Morph'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster violently morphs into a psyrus.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者猛烈地轉變為一隻賽魯斯。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Cursed Lands"
msgstr "詛咒之地"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cursed Lands'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels itself, creating a lingering curse that calls zeds in its area while enshrouds the caster with the black mist to heal and protect.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者引導自身，創造出一個持續存在的詛咒，召喚區域內的殭屍，同時用黑霧籠罩自身以進行治療和防護。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Cling"
msgstr "黏附"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cling'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster leaps onto the target's feet, harming their overall mobility.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者躍向目標的腳部，損害其整體機動性。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Shadow Push"
msgstr "暗影推擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Push'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster pushes the targets with its shadows.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者用其暗影推動目標。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Shadow Burst"
msgstr "暗影爆發"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Burst'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends out a wave of shadow, dealing moderate bashing damage, applying unstable footing and knocks them back.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者釋放出一股暗影波，造成中等鈍擊傷害，施加不穩立足效果並將其擊退。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sinister Strike"
msgstr "邪影打擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sinister Strike'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster produces a compact shadow, forming a silhouette with its claws imbued in shadows then strikes the target, dealing moderate cutting damage and applying blindness.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者產生一團凝聚的暗影，形成一個爪部浸染暗影的輪廓，然後攻擊目標，造成中等切割傷害並施加失明效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Nocturnal Sweep"
msgstr "夜影橫掃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Nocturnal Sweep'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster nimbly slashes through the vicinity, dealing moderate cutting damage to the surrounding creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者靈巧地掃過周圍區域，對附近的生物造成中等切割傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Shadow Pull"
msgstr "暗影拉扯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Pull'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body to send forth errant shadows to the targets then pulls them in.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者引導身體，向目標釋放錯亂的暗影，然後將他們拉向自己。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Refleshing Strike"
msgstr "血肉重塑打擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Refleshing Strike'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
