msgstr "血肉重塑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reflesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster shoots out tendrils that pierces nearby allies then injecting them with extra flesh, healing a moderate amount of health.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者射出觸鬚刺穿附近的盟友，然後注入額外的血肉，為其恢復中等量的生命值。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Flesh Chunk"
