"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster takes a chunk of its own flesh, dealing an enormous amount of damage on itself.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者從自身取下一塊血肉，對自己造成鉅額傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Stab"
msgstr "觸鬚刺擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Stab'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends out a tentacle to pierce at its target, doing a small random stabbing damage. This is casted 4 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者伸出一根觸鬚刺向目標，造成隨機的少量刺擊傷害。此法術會施放4次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
