#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gorespawn'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels itself to send out giant tendrils more actively, causing the ground to resonate which applies unstable footing to all creatures within its range.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者引導自身更積極地釋放巨型觸鬚，引起地面共振，使其範圍內的所有生物陷入立足不穩狀態。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Terrestrial Destruction"
msgstr "大地毀滅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Terrestrial Destruction'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster takes down adjacent terrains, destroying them which results into a deep pit.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者摧毀相鄰的地形，將其破壞成一個深坑。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tendril Disturbance"
