"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者感知到附近的目標後，在其附近釋放1-2根觸鬚。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Slam"
msgstr "觸鬚猛擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Slam'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster slams itself to the target, dealing bashing damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者猛擊目標，造成鈍擊傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Smash"
msgstr "觸鬚粉碎"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Smash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster slams itself to the ground, dealing bashing damage and applying unstable footing to the affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者猛擊地面，造成鈍擊傷害並使受影響的生物陷入立足不穩狀態。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a spell'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
msgid ""
"Target spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster locks its line of sight onto the target, then randomly casts one of the Spell(s).'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的目標法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者鎖定目標的視線，然後隨機施放其中一個法術。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Mincemeat Heal"
