msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者進行同類相食，啃咬自身或相鄰的隨機盟友，根據造成的傷害的50%額外恢復施法者的生命值。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
msgid "a note"
msgstr "一條註釋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a note'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
msgid ""
"Note spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Provides a notice about the casted spell's result.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的註釋法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'提供關於施放法術結果的提示。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Whipslash"
msgstr "鞭笞斬擊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Whipslash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's volatile lump sends forth an errant tendril that strikes the target, dealing cutting damage. This is casted randomly from 2 to 4 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者的不穩定肉塊釋放出一根錯亂的觸鬚攻擊目標，造成切割傷害。此法術會隨機施放2到4次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Corrupt"
msgstr "腐化"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Corrupt'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's arm biters vomit a corrosive, sticky fluid at the target's area that enslows and constantly damages all creatures who stands on it.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者的噬臂者向目標區域嘔吐腐蝕性粘液，使站立其上的所有生物減速並持續受到傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Core Stun"
msgstr "核心眩暈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core Stun'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster becomes stunned.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者陷入眩暈狀態。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Core Damage"
msgstr "核心傷害"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core Damage'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster takes massive bio damage, along with the constant damaging and crippling effects from the explosion.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者承受鉅額生化傷害，並持續受到爆炸造成的傷害與致殘效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Core Explosion"
msgstr "核心爆炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core Explosion'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's torsal lump suddenly explodes, spreading a large area of corrupted acid and deals tremendous bashing damage that affects all creatures within range. Caster then becomes crippled, rendering it slowed and unconscious for a long time.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者的軀幹腫塊突然爆炸，擴散大範圍腐蝕酸液，並對範圍內所有生物造成鉅額鈍擊傷害。施法者隨後陷入殘廢狀態，長時間減速且失去意識。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Pin Missile"
msgstr "針刺飛彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pin Missile'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster shoots off needle-like spikes into the target, dealing stabbing damage. Casted randomly between 2 to 7 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者向目標發射針狀尖刺，造成穿刺傷害。隨機施放2至7次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Spike Bombardment"
msgstr "尖刺轟炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Spike Bombardment'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster shoots off spikes projected into the sky, then falls down into the target, dealing moderate stabbing damage to all affected creatures in an area.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者向空中發射尖刺，隨後尖刺墜落至目標區域，對區域內所有受影響生物造成中等穿刺傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Hail of Spikes"
