#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hail of Spikes'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels itself to shoot its spike in every direction, dealing moderate stabbing damage to all affected creatures surrounding it.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者引導自身向所有方向發射尖刺，對周圍所有受影響生物造成中等穿刺傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Pressure Point"
msgstr "壓力點"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pressure Point'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster spews out its fang at its target, dealing stabbing damage to all affected creatures within a line.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者向目標噴射獠牙，對直線範圍內所有受影響生物造成穿刺傷害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Rage"
msgstr "狂暴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Rage'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's rage intensifies, drastically increasing its speed everytime it casts a spell.'"
