#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Necrotic Implosion"
msgstr "壞死內爆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Necrotic Implosion'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its inner flesh, then suddenly erupts internally. This explosion sends some flesh outwards from the gaps, creating a series of meteorites to fall down from the sky. All creatures that gets hit are inflicted with tremendous bashing damage while forming a potent living flesh under them. This is randomly casted between 20 to 40 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。若你看到此條，請閱讀以下說明：\n"
"'施法者引導體內血肉，隨後突然發生內部爆炸。爆炸使血肉從縫隙向外迸發，形成一系列隕石從天而降。被擊中的生物將承受鉅額鈍擊傷害，並在其下方生成強效活性血肉。此法術隨機施放20至40次。'"

