msgid "Heal"
msgstr "治療"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the injected target is a zombie type, heal them afterwards."
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'如果被注入的目標是殭屍類型，之後會治療他們。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Inject"
msgstr "注入"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Inject'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster injects the target, dealing minor stabbing damage."
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者注入目標，造成輕微刺擊傷害。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the injected target is a zombie type, heal them afterwards. Also provides a buff."
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'如果被注入的目標是殭屍類型，之後會治療他們。同時提供一個增益效果。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Withdraw"
msgstr "撤退"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Withdraw'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster then takes distance from the target.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者隨後與目標拉開距離。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Trigger"
msgstr "觸發"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Trigger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster unlocks the potential prowess of nearby monsters, increasing their combat abilities.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者解鎖附近怪物的潛在能力，提升其戰鬥屬性。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Dilute"
msgstr "稀釋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dilute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster stares submissively at the target, inflicting negative combat bonuses.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代說明：\n"
"'施法者順從地凝視目標，施加負面戰鬥加成。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Incite"
msgstr "煽動"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Incite'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster spreads its blob-stimulating goo through its fingers, causing the infected creature's blob to grow rapidly which increases the host's body mass, gaining combat bonuses, but makes them suffer from excessive growth.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者通過手指散佈其刺激粘液團的粘液，導致受感染生物的粘液團迅速生長，從而增加宿主體重，獲得戰鬥增益，但也會使其遭受過度生長的痛苦。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Birth'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster gives a live birth to 2-5 baby saddlers. These saddlers are filled with hidden potentials, providing them the ability to grow so much faster into a full grown combat saddler once they sense danger around them.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者活體分娩出2-5只幼年鞍背怪。這些鞍背怪蘊含著隱藏的潛力，一旦感知到周圍危險，便能迅速成長為完全成熟的戰鬥鞍背怪。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Enshroud"
msgstr "籠罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Enshroud'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
