"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends off thich shadows towards the target.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者向目標釋放濃密的陰影。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Summon Shadow"
msgstr "召喚陰影"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon Shadow'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster then split chunks of its shadow that chases down targets.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者分裂出大塊陰影碎片，追擊目標。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Shadow Enshroud"
msgstr "陰影籠罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Enshroud'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'The caster splits in every direction, covering nearby hostile targets with thicc shadows.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者向各個方向分裂，用濃密的陰影覆蓋附近的敵對目標。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "Shadow Enshroud: Blind"
msgstr "陰影籠罩：致盲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Enshroud: Blind'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Blinds target for few turns as well.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'同時使目標緻盲數回合。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid "Infect"
msgstr "感染"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Infect'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster will try to infect the target by dealing 25 biological damage. If the target dies, they succumb to the flesh.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者會嘗試感染目標，造成25點生物傷害。如果目標死亡，他們將屈服於血肉。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Infect'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster infects the target, turning them into a crimson horror.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請閱讀以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者感染目標，將其轉變為猩紅恐怖。'"

